1 A BILL for an Act to create and enact a new section to chapter 40-49 and a new subsection to
2 section 40-49-12 of the North Dakota Century Code, relating to cooperative purchasing
3 pursuant to a joint powers agreement and authorizing a board of park commissioners to engage
4 in cooperative purchasing.
5 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
6 SECTION 1. A new subsection to section 40-49-12 of the North Dakota Century Code is
7 created and enacted as follows:
8 Contract for cooperative purchases pursuant to a joint powers agreement under
9 chapter 54 - 40.3 .
10 SECTION 2. A new section to chapter 40-49 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
11 and enacted as follows:
12 Cooperative purchasing - Authorized.
13 With the approval of the board of park commissioners, a park district may participate in a
14 cooperative purchasing agreement with the state, or another political subdivision of this state or
15 any other state, by executing a joint powers agreement under chapter 54 - 40.3. This section
16 does not apply to construction of a public improvement as defined in chapter 48 - 01.2 .
